docs.lead_paragraph: President Clinton and Senator Bob Dole started scrapping today over health insurance and it was clear that they saw a major Presidential campaign confrontation in the making.

headline.main: Clinton-Dole Fight on Health Bill Is Preview of Campaign to Come
